---
title: Spicy-Sweet Szechuan Shrimp Lo Mein with Bell Pepper & Peanuts
description: For a flavorful noodle stir-fry with a touch of heat, put down the takeout menu and look no further than your own kitchen! You’ll toss tender lo mein noodles with portobello mushrooms, onion, and bell pepper in a sweet-umami sauce of honey, miso, and Szechuan paste. A final sprinkling of crunchy peanuts makes this bowl sing!
